quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  74,32,Sivyo none ? Ndarahiye k’ukwezi
  74,33,N’Ijoro rikeye
  74,34,No mugitondo hakeye
  74,35,Mu vy’ukuri uwo muriro udahera n’umwe mungorane niniya zihambaye cane
  74,36,N’igabisho ku bantu
  74,37,K’uwushaka muri mwebwe n’atanguze kuja imbere canke aje inyuma
  74,38,"Umutima\tw’umwumwe\twese\tuzo\tkwugaranirwa\tmu\tmuriro\tudahera kubera ibikorwa bibi wakoze"
  74,39,Dukuye mwo abantu b’iburyo
  74,40,Abo bantu bazoba mu mirima babazanya
  74,41,Kubera abantu babi
  74,42,N’ikintu nyabaki cabatwaye mu muriro udahera
  74,43,"Bazo vuga bati:- ntitwari mu bantu bahora basenga"
  74,44,Kandi ntitwahora duha abakene ibifungugwa
  74,45,Kandi twahora twibira mu bicumuro hamwe n’abahora bibira
  74,46,Kandi twahora duhakana yuko ata musi w’uguciribwa imanza
  74,47,Kugeza n’aho dushikirwa n’urupfu
  74,48,Ntaco bizofasha uko gusaba kw’abasabira abaribo bose
  74,49,Mbega bafise iki ? Ntibitaho kuri rino tuza
  74,50,Nkuko umengo n’indogobwe zigenda ningoga na ningoga
  74,51,Ziruka nk’intare
  74,52,"Umwe wese muribo\tagomba yuko ahabwa impapuro zizoba zanditswe ko"
  74,53,Oya! kuri bo ntibatinya umuhero w’Isi
  74,54,"Oya ! Si uko, mu vy’ukuri ubwo n’ubwibutso"
  74,55,Rero uwushaka azokwibuka
  74,56,"Ntibazo kwibuka atari uko Imana yabishatse, kuko niyo ikwiwe gutinywa n’ukugira imbabazi"